## Quick start (worker + FastAPI)

See `.cursor/skills/celery-redis-jobs/setup.md` for full setup: config, worker, FastAPI app, run commands (Redis, worker, API), and how to trigger tasks from HTTP. For the full stack (Postgres, OpenAI), add `DATABASE_URL` and `OPENAI_API_KEY`; see `.cursor/skills/celery-redis-jobs/reference.md` for full code samples.
